if ! exists(':Abolish')
  finish
endif

" Shorthands
Abolish pub public

Abolish pro protected
Abolish prot protected

Abolish pri private
Abolish priv private
Abolish prv private

Abolish fn function
Abolish fun function

" Common misspellings
Abolish anohter another
Abolish antoher another
Abolish aray array
Abolish eixt exit
Abolish naem name
Abolish pritn print
Abolish retrun return

" Lazy hands
Abolish 4this $this
Abolish 2param @param
Abolish 2return @return
